51
00:05:30,333 --> 00:05:36,153
The interest in the road sector  
is that we have on one side

52
00:05:36,153 --> 00:05:42,223
a representation on a plane 

53
00:05:42,223 --> 00:05:46,463
and essentially, 
as the road is a linear object,

54
00:05:46,463 --> 00:05:51,533
it can also be represented
in a one-dimensional space. 

55
00:05:51,671 --> 00:05:57,211
We speak here of a tensile axis
type of representation,

56
00:05:57,211 --> 00:06:03,681
ie the geometry here on 
my path on the plane

